Fill a @cup{} with liquid of your choice (we recommend @milk{} or @water{}).

Pour @Peachy Mango Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{1%unit}, @Banana Berry Ready-to-Blend
Smoothie{2%units}, @Acai-Cherry Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{1%unit},
@Cocoa Banana Nut Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{1%unit}, and
@Tropical Greens Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{1%unit} into #blender{}; blend until
smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!

> To ensure the highest quality when you receive your smoothies, they will come in
> a separate box from your meals. Your Ready-to-Blend Smoothie box may arrive
> a few days after your meal box. Smoothies should be stored frozen.

> To enjoy these fruit-packed, no-sugar-added blends, all you have to do is blend
> them with the liquid of your choice (we like milk) until smooth and enjoy!